definitions.definition: A type of fortification , like a hornwork , but consisting of a full bastion with the walls on either side ending in half-bastions from which longer flank walls run back towards the main fortress.

main_definition: ( countable ) A type of fortification , like a hornwork , but consisting of a full bastion with the walls on either side ending in half-bastions from which longer flank walls run back towards the main fortress.
secondary_definitions: ( dentistry , uncountable ) The addition of a crown .
